Title: GoLive Probiotics for Women
Body (HTML): Convenient, multi-strain blends developed formulated by microbiologists and dietitians to ensure the most effective probiotic products available in any form. GOLIVE products are freeze-dried and maintained in our patented, foil packaging to ensure they are LIVE and growing when it matters most: when you consume them!. A Smarter Way to Probiotic. Only real, live and growing probiotics to consume as nature intended and as we used to before pasteurization, preservation, irradiation: in a dynamic, live and growing state. Accompanied only by organic and non-GMO prebiotic soluble fibers and other complementary ingredients. No pills, no capsules, no gummies, no yogurts, no fermented beverages (most of which contain only yeast and spores, including Bacillus coagulans)and no B.S. A Healthier Way to Hydrate. Mix a packet of GOLIVE in your water, juice, smoothie or other food or beverage. Or think outside the bottle and look inside the cap, then pop it to release probiotics into our delicious, low-calorie beverages. Take your pick of our lightly-sweetened, lightly-flavored ready-to-drink beverages and powder blends, or enjoy our flavorless products. Either way, Go With Your Gut and GOLIVE! Real. Live. Probiotics. GOLIVE products contain only well-researched, human-commensurate strains (mainly Lactos and Bifidos) that persist in the human gut. Unfortunately for consumers, many products with probiotics on their labels contain Bacillus coagulans or other spores that do not persist in the human gut. Alive Growing GOLIVE formulations and packaging are designed to emulate nature to ensure you consume probiotics in a live and growing state, as nature intended. Products in a static state (e.g., pills, capsules) or post-fermented state (e.g., kombuchas, yogurts, kefirs) simply cannot do the same. We GUT You Covered on the prebiotics and live probiotics.
